       <p class="text-center">
        Although you can use the red buttons to add tone marks, we highly recommend you use the number method (e.g. hao3) for speed and placement of the accent above the correct vowel. [Hint: Type "v" for "ü"]

					</div>	 
				</td>
				<td class="cantype hide pinyin div-cantonese" style="text-align: center;">
					{{if allchar.yale == null || allchar.yale == 'None'}}<i><font style="font-size: 17px;color:#acacac;">n/a</font></i>{{else}}{{allchar.yale}}{{/if}}
				</td>

					{{if allchar.jyutping == null || allchar.jyutping == 'None'}}<i><font style="font-size: 17px;color:#acacac;">n/a</font></i>{{else}}{{allchar.jyutping}}{{/if}}
				</td>
				<td class="txt-cell">{{allchar.definition}}</td>

									data-color="nonecontent"
									data-sc="same"
									data-tc="same"></span></li>
					{{else}}
					{{if allchar.sc != allchar.tc}}
					{{each allchar.tc.split('') as eachallchar eachindex}}
						<li><span class="smbl singlechar {{allchar.pinyin | bothcolorclfrompycoo : eachindex}} colorspan"
									data-dcolor="smpl"
									data-color="{{allchar.pinyin | bothcolorclfrompy : eachindex}}"
									data-sc="{{allchar.sc.charAt(eachindex)}}"
									data-tc="{{allchar.tc.charAt(eachindex)}}"></span></li>
					{{/each}}						
					{{else}}
						<li><span class="smbl singlechar nonecontent same"
									data-dcolor="nonecontent"

					{{/if}}

					</ul>
				</td>
		
			</tr>
			{{/each}}
			{{each mdbgEn as allchar index}}
			<tr class="fn-en">
				
				<td class="smbl-cstm-wrp tbl-wrap  word" class2="hidden-xs hidden-sm">
				  {{if allchar.pinyin == null}}

				  {{else}}
                  <table class="table-inner">

										data-color="{{allchar.pinyin | bothcolorclfrompy : eachindex}}"

										data-tc="{{allchar.tc.charAt(eachindex)}}"></span></a>{{/each}}
							</li>
                          </ul>
                        </td>
                        {{if allchar.sc.length == 1 || allchar.sc.length == 2}}
                        <td class="learn-link-wrap">

                    </tbody>
                  </table>
                  {{/if}}

					{{else}}
